"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"

#. ﻿INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_01
msgid "In the early 1900's,\\na dark shadow covered a small\\ncountry town in rural America."
msgstr "在20世纪初，\\n一片黑暗的阴影笼罩了美国乡村的一座小镇。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_02
msgid "The dark shadow formed\\nmysteriously at the\\nsummit of Mt Itoi."
msgstr "这片黑暗的阴影\\n在糸井山的山顶神秘地凝聚成形。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_03
msgid "At that time,\\nnumerous paranormal\\nincidents occured."
msgstr "那时，超自然事件\\n频发不止。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_04
msgid "The last incident\\ninvolved the disappearance\\nof a young married couple."
msgstr "最后一次事件\\n涉及到一对年轻夫妇\\n的离奇失踪。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_05
msgid "The man's name was George.\\nThe woman's name was Maria."
msgstr "丈夫名为乔治。\\n妻子名为玛丽亚。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_06
msgid "As soon as they disappeared,\\nso did the dark shadow."
msgstr "他们消失的那一刻，\\n黑暗的阴影也随之散去。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_07
msgid "Two years later,\\nas suddenly as he left,\\nGeorge returned."
msgstr "两年后，\\n乔治回来了，\\n来得和他当初离开时一样突然。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_08
msgid "He never told anyone\\nwhere he had been\\nor what he had done."
msgstr "他从未向任何人透露\\n自己去了哪里\\n又都做了什么。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_09
msgid "But he began an odd\\nstudy of psychic powers,\\nall by himself."
msgstr "但随后\\n他开始独自进行\\n奇异的灵能研究。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_10
msgid "As for Maria,\\nhis wife..."
msgstr "至于玛丽亚，\\n他的妻子···"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_11
msgid "She never returned."
msgstr "她再也没有回来。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_OLD_12
msgid "80 years have passed\\nsince then."
msgstr "自那之后，\\n时间过去了80年。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_NOW_01
msgid "The year is 1988."
msgstr "时间来到1988年。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_NOW_02
msgid "Outside Podunk, a small town in America."
msgstr "美国的一座小镇，波顿克的郊外。"

#. INTRO_CUTSCENE_PUNCTUATION
msgid ".,;:…!?"
msgstr "。，；：···！？"

